Flag riscv
 Description: Build with riscv backend
 Default: true

Library riscv_plugin
  XMETADescription: provide the RISC-V disassembler
  Path:          plugins/riscv
  Build$:        flag(everything) || flag(riscv)
  BuildDepends:  bap
  FindlibName:   bap-riscv
  CCOpt:         $cc_optimization
  CCLib:         $riscv_lib $cxxlibs $riscv_ldflags
  CSources:      bap_riscv.h,
                 bap_riscv.cc,
                 strings.h,
                 strings.cc
  FindlibName:   bap-plugin-riscv
  InternalModules: Riscv_main
  XMETAExtraLines: tags="disassembler"

